:0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:11:24.000Z","msg":"其實有冇巫師/偏門方法可以做低佢 至少令佢百病纏身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ac88bcb290b93764eb924fad4a318ac5f96730","tid":1422610,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"分享另一招對付藍色父母 我同原文主角一樣響wts同老豆母講自己幾絕望 人生咁灰 佢地始終錫我 琴晚都軟化開始講返啲人話<br />\n<br />\n（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n我尋日發現左一招有用既，就係威脅唔生小朋友，我媽成日指罵我無聊，去遊行，去連儂牆，又話我偏激。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢講依家已經無動力生仔，因為生出黎會俾白衣人同警察打。又講我同老公每年交幾多幾多稅俾政府，但原來佢地係會打我地下一代bla bla bla. <br />\n<br />\n我媽無回應，但正常媽媽聽到錢就會緊張d,仲要搞到佢無得抱孫。<br />\n<br />\n尋晚，初見成效，見到媽媽睇rthk, 我離開左，返黎都無轉台。 唔知有無用，但抱孫依點應該係老人家著緊既。"},{"pid":"ddcfd9948c15627de5c56257ef6e000194b7bf94","tid":1422610,"uid":5422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"唔好影啦豬豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c38c19f06ea0a76a6c79270ab433cbf2574604","tid":1422610,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4f1134a97c36b79edf26a5c52ab06d0c144984","tid":1422610,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"自推其實同打飛機冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560c734e07e08cb20e9fef6eb5221051930c53cc","tid":1422610,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d4f1134a97c36b79edf26a5c52ab06d0c144984","tid":1422610,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"自推其實同打飛機冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"係直頭冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759e7d7c3b431ac53246b8a50b59ea4d02072081","tid":1422610,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12: